variable.name: Notch1
variable.description: Translocation associated notch homolog (sample type: plasma)
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for NOTCH1 is 3.35E+01 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 2.47E+04 pg/mL. NOTCH1 values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use NOTCH1_I to see what records are below and above these limits. NOTCH1 values were set to unknown if NOTCH1_CV was greater than or equal to 48.6 for Offspring (IDTYPE= 1) or 49.4 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3)

variable.name: Notch1_CV
variable.description: CV for translocation associated notch homolog
variable.comment: NOTCH1 values were set to unknown if NOTCH1_CV was greater than or equal to 48.6 for Offspring (IDTYPE= 1) or 49.4 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3)

variable.name: CSF2RB
variable.description: Colony stimulating factor 2 receptor, beta, low-affinity (granulocyte-macrophage) (sample type: plasma)
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for CSF2RB is 1.94E+02 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 1.43E+05 pg/mL. CSF2RB values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use CSF2RB_I to see what records are below and above these limits. CSF2RB values were set to unknown if CSF2RB_CV was greater than or equal to 102.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE= 1) or 107.0 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3)

variable.name: CSF2RB_CV
variable.description: CV for colony stimulating factor 2 receptor, beta, low-affinity (granulocyte-macrophage)
variable.comment: CSF2RB values were set to unknown if CSF2RB_CV was greater than or equal to 102.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE= 1) or 107.0 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3)

variable.name: FLT3
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for FLT3 is 4.49E+03 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 3.33E+06 pg/mL. FLT3 values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use FLT3_I to see what records are below and above these limits. FLT3 values were set to unknown if FLT3_CV was greater than or equal to 116.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE= 1) or 113.0 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3)

variable.name: FLT3_CV
variable.comment: FLT3 values were set to unknown if FLT3_CV was greater than or equal to 116.0 for Offspring (IDTYPE= 1) or 113.0 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3)

variable.name: IDS
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for IDS is 1.17E+04 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 8.44E+06 pg/mL. IDS values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use IDS to see what records are below and above these limits. No outliers for either cohort or both cohorts combined.

variable.name: IDS_CV
variable.comment: No outliers for either cohort or both cohorts combined.

variable.name: WNK1
variable.description: WNK lysine deficient protein kinase 1 (sample type: plasma)
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for WNK1 is 4.45E+01 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 3.35E+04 pg/mL. WNK1 values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use WNK1_I to see what records are below and above these limits. WNK1 values were set to unknown if WNK1_CV was greater than or equal to 126.0 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3)

variable.name: WNK1_CV
variable.description: CV for WNK lysine deficient protein kinase 1
variable.comment: WNK1 values were set to unknown if WNK1_CV was greater than or equal to 126.0 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3)
